############################################################################
#
# Arcadia is a visualisation tool for metabolic pathways
# This file is a shell script to finish the installation of the arcadia1.0
# application on MacOSX
# It just copies the content of the res directory into the Resources part
# of the .app folder (and discards any old version)
# 
